com/civilservantsflowers</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做"},{"pid":"c12f7a4ef92f36785076b36c5a05ae0b2b25b1bb","tid":1361743,"uid":65854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:33:03.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"9778303914a2cdb8acbbf8dfc6394d25d11ee91c","tid":1361743,"uid":40078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:51:31.000Z","msg":"bu好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b50dc2a483366886e9070333c47efde8ef8f12b","tid":1361743,"uid":272775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:23:03.000Z","msg":"仲有我哋！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n[遍地開花] 貿發局100+員工：香港加油<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1365434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1365434</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}